properties.name: booking.cache.maxEntries
properties.description: Sets the maximum objects to be held in local cache (0 = no limit).

properties.name: booking.cache.memoryStorePolicy
properties.description: Sets the eviction policy (LRU, LFU or FIFO). An invalid argument will set it to LRU.

properties.name: booking.cache.maxTimeToIdle
properties.description: The maximum number of seconds an element can exist in the cache without being accessed (0 = no limit).

properties.name: booking.cache.maxTimeToLive
properties.description: The maximum number of seconds an element can exist in the cache regardless of use (0 = no limit).

properties.name: booking.cache.eternal
